  Department of Computer Engineering, San Jos\'e State University\\
  \texttt{andrew.bond@sjsu.edu} ~\textbar~ ORCID: 0009-0003-2599-6158}

## LaTeX (TMLR / JMLR \name style)
\author{\name Andrew H. Bond, \emph{Senior Member, IEEE} \email andrew.bond@sjsu.edu \\
  \addr Department of Computer Engineering \\ San Jos\'e State University \\
  ORCID: 0009-0003-2599-6158}

Do not use agi.hpc@gmail.com on papers. For anonymized (double-blind) submissions the
venue style hides the byline automatically; keep the full block in source.
